Package: nucdataBaynet
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian networks for nuclear data evaluation
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Georg Schnabel [aut,cre]
Maintainer: Georg Schnabel <georg.schnabel@nucleardata.com>
Description: This package enables the creation of and inference in
    Bayesian networks with multivariate normal conditional distributions
    and linear and non-linear functional relationships between nodes.
